within them all.

00:28:05.730 --> 00:28:09.130
So we see that there
really isn't any division.

00:28:09.130 --> 00:28:12.900
Instead, we have a unification
of the scientific world

00:28:12.900 --> 00:28:14.700
of our daily experience

00:28:14.700 --> 00:28:18.360
